// video
Hello guys, in this video I will show you how to give slope to your intersections.
to do that: uncheck flat junctions ... of ONLY the two segments that are part of the main road.
Notice that the segments on the side are twisted sideways to match the slope of the intersection.
there are a couple of things you can do to fine tune your intersection.
1- the sideway twist on this road continues until the next node. I create a node near the intersection to limit the reach of the twist.
2- now the cars entering this segment are driving UP the intersection. therefore we need to give slope to this segment to avoid suddent changes of slope.
thats it guys. have fun with your intersection slopes.
